org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.job

Interface JobInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JobInfoImpl, JobInfoImpl

    @PublicAPI
public interface JobInfo
extends Serializable
    JobInfo provides information about the Job it is linked with.
    These information and only them are able to change inside the Job.
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 0.9
